{
  "id": "5ee265077ee8d5002047fc59",
  "title": "1人→2人→全体",
  "created": 1591895320,
  "updated": 1591895354,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ee265077ee8d5002047fc59",
      "text": "1人→2人→全体",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895320,
      "updated": 1591895320
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26518aff09e0000dfa27f",
      "text": ">基本は「[1人→2人→全体]」です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895320,
      "updated": 1591895321
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26518aff09e0000dfa280",
      "text": "[/shiology/05129-180512 大教室でも「教えあい」によるアクティブ・ラーニングを実践する授業の手法]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895321,
      "updated": 1591895321
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26518aff09e0000dfa281",
      "text": "これは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895321,
      "updated": 1591895321
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26518aff09e0000dfa282",
      "text": "\tまず自分一人で紙に自分の考えを書く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895321,
      "updated": 1591895321
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26518aff09e0000dfa283",
      "text": " 次に2人組の相手方にその考えを説明する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895321,
      "updated": 1591895321
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26518aff09e0000dfa284",
      "text": " 最後に教室で全体に対して発表する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895321,
      "updated": 1591895321
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26518aff09e0000dfa285",
      "text": "というプロセス。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895321,
      "updated": 1591895321
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26518aff09e0000dfa286",
      "text": "いきなり全体に対して発表することは心理的ハードルが高い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895321,
      "updated": 1591895350
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26536aff09e0000dfa288",
      "text": "1人で紙に書いてみること、1人に話してみること、はハードルが低い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1591895350,
      "updated": 1591895354
    },
    {
      "id": "5ee26539aff09e0000dfa289",
